            <title>[FELIX-1516] Child instances use stuff from the /etc directory in the root</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1516</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I create a new instance with admin:create.&lt;br/&gt;
Then, to make sure it only uses its own configuration, I temporary rename the etc directory in the parent.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now I start up the child instance and get an exception:&lt;br/&gt;
K:\assembly\target\apache-felix-karaf-1.2.0-SNAPSHOT\instances\too&amp;gt;bin\karaf.bat&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;karaf.bat: Ignoring predefined value for KARAF_HOME&lt;br/&gt;
